[x] Abs Value: Can it handle |x|?

[x] Constants: Are π and e recognized?

[ ] Implicit Mult: Does 2x, x y, and 2sin(x) work?

[x] Comma Support: Does min(x, y, z) work for multiple args?

[ ] Domain Handling: If the parser sees 1/0 or sqrt(-1), does the evaluator crash or return NaN?

[ ] Scientific Notation: Can it parse 1e-5 or 2.5E6?

[ ] Implicit Leading Zero: Does .5 get parsed as 0.5?

[ ] Keep in pi-notation: Can we display 2pi instead of 6.283185307179586?

[ ] Nice error handling: Standardize error messages for syntax errors, undefined variables, and math errors.